@node KEYS "ShimmerDB:  Hotkeys"

@{u}@{b}HotKeys@{ub}@{uu}
  Keyboard hotkeys are unavailable when a string gadget is active; except
for Tab-cycling and command-execution.
  Menu shortcuts from within string gadgets may work, but may also result
in extra data being entered, or may be intercepted by the string gadget itself.
A little cleanup is needed here.

@{u}@{b}Main Window Hotkeys:@{ub}@{uu}
- <Tab>        - Cycle to next string gadget.
  <Shift><tab> - Cycle to previous string gadget.  A little more work is
                 needed here.
- <Return>        - From a data string gadget, cycle to next string gadget.
  <Shift><Return> - Cycle to previous string gadget.
    <Return> and <Shift><Return> currently work better than Tab cycling.

- <CRSR UP>   - Selects previous item in listview.
- <CRSR DOWN> - Selects next item in listview.
    Multiple items may be selected by holding down the <Shift> key.

- f           - Cycle forwards through field list.
  <Shift> f   - Cycle backwards through field list.
- r           - Cycle forwards through record list.
  <Shift> r   - Cycle backwards through record list.
- e           - Cycle forwards through the @{"edit types" link GUI_ETYP} (Fields, Records, Text).
  <Shift> e   - Cycle backwards through the @{"edit types" link GUI_ETYP} (Fields, Records, Text).
- m           - Cycle forwards through the @{"edit modes" link GUI_EMOD} (Add, Edit, Insert...).
  <Shift> m   - Cycle backwards through the @{"edit modes" link GUI_EMOD} (Add, Edit, Insert...).
    When the last/first item is reached, will wrap around to the first/last
    item.


@{u}@{b}Search Requester Hotkeys:@{ub}@{uu}
- f (or F)  - Find the next occurrence of the current search pattern.
- n (or N)  - Find the previous occurrence of the current search pattern.


@{u}@{b}Menu Shortcuts:@{ub}@{uu}
  Listed in menu descritions.  Some may be changed in future versions.
@endnode

